    <td valign="top">
     <p align=center><font size="+2"><b><i>6502Em</i></b></font></p>
     <p align=center><img src="/murklesoft/riscos/exile.gif" alt="man from Exile"></p>  

<p>If you are using an Iyonix, you may need to install a suitable
640x500 mode so that MODE 7 works. You also need to have a working MODE 21 (640x512).

<p>Here are a couple of 640x512 modes and the corresponding modified
640x500 modes. You can either use these or modify a 640x512 of
your own similarly.

<pre>
# 640 x 512 (60Hz)
startmode
mode_name:640 x 512
x_res:640
y_res:512
pixel_rate:32000
h_timings:64,76,30,640,30,30
v_timings:3,16,40,512,40,4
sync_pol:3
endmode

# 640 x 500 (60Hz)
startmode
mode_name:640 x 500
x_res:640
y_res:500
pixel_rate:32000
h_timings:64,76,36,640,36,30
v_timings:3,16,40,500,40,4
sync_pol:3
endmode

# 640 x 512 (70Hz)
startmode
mode_name:640 x 512
x_res:640
y_res:512
pixel_rate:37500
h_timings:64,76,30,640,30,30
v_timings:3,16,40,512,40,4
sync_pol:3
endmode

# 640 x 500 (70Hz)
startmode
mode_name:640 x 500
x_res:640
y_res:500
pixel_rate:37500
h_timings:64,76,36,640,36,30
v_timings:3,16,40,500,40,4
sync_pol:3
endmode

</pre>

